@page
@model IndexModel
@{
    ViewData[ "Title" ] = "Home page";
}

<div class="text-center my-4">
    <img src="~/img/logo.png" alt="egoPdf" class="img-fluid" style="max-height: 320px;" />
</div>


<div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
        <h2>Description</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>
                This is an automated port of FPF for PHP. Some parts have been recoded but many others are still as given.
            </li>
            <li>
                This is not a full fledged tool, but instead if is intendend to be used as last resource. If everything else fails or is too heavy and you have some time to spend, then, maybe this is for you.
            </li>

            <li>
                Should you use it? Probably not. Its mantained just for fun. But if you like the DIY approach, then maybe it will suit you.
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
        <h2>
            Tutorial
        </h2>
        <p>
            Currently, egoPdf status is work in progress. First milestone is to recreate all samples
            in the FPDF <a href="https://www.fpdf.org/en/tutorial/index.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">tutorial</a>.
        </p>
        <table class="table table-bordered table-hover">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>
                    </th>
                    <th>
                        Original FPDF sample
                    </th>
                    <th>
                        egoPdf implementation & variations
                    </th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <b>Sample 1</b>. Minimal example
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <a href="https://www.fpdf.org/en/tutorial/tuto1.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Tutorial 1</a>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <a (click)="download($event)" href="/api/SampleData/GetSample1">Tutorial 1</a>
                        <i class="icon-list-alt sampleSource link_out" data-sample="1"></i>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <b>Sample 2</b>. Header, footer, page break and image
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <a href="https://www.fpdf.org/en/tutorial/tuto2.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Tutorial 2</a>
                    </td>
                    <td>
